  19 Nov 2004; Simone Gotti <motaboy@gentoo.org>
  +files/kbiff-3.7-configure-arts.patch, kbiff-3.7.ebuild:
  Added a patch to the configure script to honor the "arts" USE flag. Fixes
  bug #69532.

  25 Sep 2004; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> kbiff-3.7.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc.

  22 Sep 2004; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> kbiff-3.7.ebuild:
  Stable on x86

  18 Jul 2004; Daniel Ahlberg <aliz@gentoo.org> kbiff-3.7.ebuild:
  Added amd64 keyword. Closing #52424.

  29 Jun 2004; Carsten Lohrke <carlo@gentoo.org> kbiff-3.6.3.ebuild,
